cargo-nextest 0.9.140 (a9fef2964 2026-07-05), installed prebuilt from get.nexte.st

  export CARGO_TARGET_DIR=/tmp/tb-bfd
  cargo nextest list -p zenav1-aom-dsp --cargo-profile test-fast   # warm the build
  /usr/bin/time -f "%e" cargo nextest run -p zenav1-aom-dsp --cargo-profile test-fast

Result: 341 tests run / 341 passed / 1 skipped, 12.07 s wall (nextest's own summary:
